name: The I Ching of High Tech
description:
A collection of 54 words for discovering potent new technology concepts.

Yes, for all of you earning your soylent in the disruptive, cutting-edge space of high-tech (or just marketing): the 'I Ching of High Tech' will ideate fresh and 1000% cliché-free buzzwords to lend your next white paper necessary leverage points, or simply buy you time until there is an actual product. 

You're welcome——and always stay agile!
